WEBVTT

00:10.343 --> 00:15.933
We must break free from
the petty politics of the past.

00:16.015 --> 00:19.556
America is a nation of believers

00:19.645 --> 00:25.395
that is being led by a group
of censors, critics and cynics.

00:27.110 --> 00:33.410
All of the people telling you, "You
can't have the country you want,"

00:33.491 --> 00:37.161
are the same people
that wouldn't stand...

00:37.245 --> 00:42.835
I mean, they said, "Trump doesn't
have a chance of being here tonight."

00:43.501 --> 00:45.961
Oh, we love defeating
those people, don't we?

00:46.046 --> 00:47.546
Don't we love defeating them?

00:50.342 --> 00:54.682
To all Americans
tonight, I make this promise.

00:55.347 --> 00:59.017
We will make America safe again.

00:59.101 --> 01:03.311
We will make
America strong again.

01:04.480 --> 01:07.741
And we will make
America great again!

01:07.818 --> 01:10.278
God bless you and good night!

01:10.362 --> 01:11.492
I love you.

